    (29,3,'Cliffs of Insanity','weaver','2007-03-24',4100,'','5','it was good...got a couple ok rides... probably would be better if it was lower..',0,'2019-09-10 12:03:55 -0400', '2019-09-10 12:03:55 -0400'),
    (29,3,'Cliffs of Insanity','weaver','2007-03-31',3800,'','4','mike said it was not that good at this level...still pretty powered up..',0,'2019-09-10 12:03:55 -0400', '2019-09-10 12:03:55 -0400'),
